<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Car Trading App</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alfa+Slab+One&family=Bebas+Neue&family=Bungee+Shade&family=Carter+One&family=Rowdies:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <a href="/" class="home"> TBD </a>
        <section class="header-btns">
            <section>
                <ul>
                  <li class="links"><a href="/views/buy.handlebars"> Buy </a></li>
                  <li class="links"><a href="/views/sell.handlebars"> Sell </a></li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            {{#if logged_in}}
            <button class="logout-btn" id="logout"> Logout </button>
            {{else}}
            <button class="login-btn" id="login" onclick="window.location.href='/views/login.handlebars'"> Login </button>
            {{/if}}
            <button ></button>
        </section>
    </header>

    <main>
        <form class="search">
            <h1> Welcome </h1>
            <h2> What are you looking for? </h2>
            <!-- From: https://codepen.io/stoic25/pen/gKLXWZ -->
            <section class="form-group fg--search">
                <input type="text" class="input" placeholder="Search">
                <button type="submit"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
            </section>
        </form>

        <section class="buttons">
            <button type="button" class="listing-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/views/sell.handlebars'"> Create a Listing </button>
        </section>
        
        <section class="display-postings">
            <h3> Your postings </h3>
            <p><a href="/views/login.handlebars" class="login-link">Login</a> to view.</p>
            <p> (For each posting, add to postings section - figure out functionality) </p>
            {{#if logged_in}}
            {{#each listings as |listing|}}
            <section class=""> 

            </section>

        </section>

        <section class="listings">
            <h3> Previously viewed listings </h3>
            <p><a href="/views/login.handlebars" class="login-link">Login</a> to view.</p>
            <p> (For each listing viewed, add to listings section - figure out functionality) </p>
        </section>

        <section class="faq">
            <h3> Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) </h3>
                <li class="question"> 1. Is there a posting fee? </li>
                <li class="answer"> There is no posting fee! You can post on our site completely free! </li>
                <li class="question"> 2. How do I post a successful ad? </li>
                <section class="answer"> 
                    <li> Provide an honest description of the car that you are selling.</li> 
                    <li> Include as much of the specifications of the car as you can (i.e. the model, the year it was made, the mileage, etc.). </li>
                    <li> Do some research and check and see what other people have listed their vehicle at and get an idea of the price range that you want to list your car for. </li>
                </section>
                <li class="question"> 3. How can I ensure a safe transaction? </li>
                <li class="answer"> You ALWAYS want to meet in person to avoid any potential fraud, bring a friend or a third party to accompany you. To ensure the safest transaction, meet them at a parking area of a police station. </li>
                <li class="question"> 4. What are some things to look for from a used car? </li>
                <li class="answer"> We have filters that you can use to filter your search! </li>
